		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This sounds like it'd be the perfect job for NES 2.0 variant codes (SSSS in <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/NES_2.0#Mapper_variant" class="postlink">the spec</a>). Someone go get kevtris to allocate codes for the different behavior variants.

		

